                            <comment id="446077" author="adilger" created="Thu, 27 Feb 2025 18:44:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It would also be useful to add an alias &quot;&lt;tt&gt;&amp;#45;&amp;#45;nonblock&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; in addition to &quot;&lt;tt&gt;&amp;#45;&amp;#45;non&amp;#45;block&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; for ease of use.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="446075" author="adilger" created="Thu, 27 Feb 2025 18:43:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This is even more true today, that &lt;tt&gt;&amp;#45;&amp;#45;block&lt;/tt&gt; should be the exception rather than the rule, since Lustre 2.8 servers are long behind us at this point.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
